oslo.rootwrap (1.2.0-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Build depends on iproute2, because the unit test is doing some tests using
    /sbin/ip. Thanks to Lucas Nussbaum for the bug report (Closes: #759977).
  * Added extend-diff-ignore = "^[^/]*[.]egg-info/" to d/source/options, to be
    able to build twice.

 -- Thomas Goirand <zigo@debian.org>  Mon, 01 Sep 2014 04:06:21 +0000

oslo.rootwrap (1.2.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed wrong VCS URLs.
  * Added Python 3 support.
  * Runs unit tests on build, build-conflicts with other python-osolo.*
    packages which are on the same namespace, and then preventing from doing
    "import oslo.rootwrap" from the current dir.

 -- Thomas Goirand <zigo@debian.org>  Sun, 03 Aug 2014 14:45:45 +0000

